data.description: Fantastic home on double cul-de-sac in China Spring ISD. This 3 bedroom, 2 1/2 bathroom with formal dining area offers so much space with the upstairs extra loft living area.  Kitchen offers open concept to breakfast area and living room, granite countertops, and large walk-in pantry. Large Master bedroom with en suite bath featuring dual vanity, tiled shower and soaking tub.  Great entertaining under covered patio with full privacy fenced backyard. Bonus, the play set stays.
